Create a service to be run in the swarm
#docker service create --replicas 1 --name test <image>

List the services
#docker service ls

Scale a running service
#docker service scale <service name> <number>
or
#docker service update --replica=10 <service name>

Rollback changes made to the service configuration
#docker service rollback 

Inspect a service
#docker service inspect <service name>

Docker service - replicated vs global - a global service is on that runs on all nodes while replicated service runs the specific number of replicas.

